msgid ""
"Sorry, WireShare couldn't read your old downloads.  You can restart them by "
"clicking 'Try Again' on the downloads.  When WireShare finds a source for "
"the file, the download will pick up where it left off."
msgstr ""
"Maaf, WireShare tidak dapat membaca muat turun lama anda.  Anda boleh "
"memulakan balik mereka dengan menekan 'Try Again' pada muat turunan.  "
"Apabila WireShare menjumpai sumber bagi fail, fail akan bermula dimana ia "
"berhenti."

#: components/gnutella-core/src/main/java/com/limegroup/gnutella/DownloadManagerImpl.java:284
