"them by clicking 'Try Again' on the downloads.  When WireShare finds a "
"source for the file, the download will pick up where it left off."
msgstr ""
"Maaf, WireShare tidak dapat membaca beberapa muat turun lama anda.  Anda "
"boleh memulakan balik mereka dengan menekan 'Try Again' pada muat turunan.  "
"Apabila WireShare menjumpai sumber bagi fail, fail akan bermula dimana ia "
"berhenti."

